          <briefdescription>
<para>Configure specific operation for Quad-SPI nor flash. </para>
          </briefdescription>
          <detaileddescription>
<para>It configures specific operation for Quad-SPI nor flash such as lock or unlock UMA mode, set write protection pin of internal flash, and so on.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>in</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Pointer to a <ref refid="structnpcx__ex__ops__qspi__oper__in" kindref="compound">npcx_ex_ops_qspi_oper_in</ref> structure specifying the operation to set. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
          </detaileddescription>
        </enumvalue>
